file.content:
components:
  schemas:
    tmp0:
      properties:
        errorMessage: {type: string}
        successful: {type: string}
      type: object
    tmp1:
      properties:
        errorMessage: {type: string}
        successful: {type: string}
      type: object
    tmp2:
      properties:
        errorMessage: {type: string}
        successful: {type: string}
      type: object
    tmp3:
      properties:
        errorMessage: {type: string}
        json: {type: string}
        successful: {type: string}
      type: object
    tmp4:
      properties:
        errorMessage: {type: string}
        successful: {type: string}
        usernames: {type: string}
      type: object
    tmp5:
      properties:
        errorMessage: {type: string}
        successful: {type: string}
      type: object
    tmp6:
      properties:
        errorMessage: {type: string}
        successful: {type: string}
      type: object
  securitySchemes: {}
info:
  contact: {email: frikky@shuffler.io, name: '@frikkylikeme', url: 'https://twitter.com/frikkylikeme'}
  description: Automated generation of Slack Slack
  title: Slack Slack
  version: 1.0.0
  x-logo: data:image/png;base64,
openapi: 3.0.2
paths:
  tmp0:
    post:
      description: Archive A Conversation
      parameters:
      - description: Archives a conversation by channel name
        example: random
        in: query
        name: Channel Name
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {$ref: '#/components/schemas/tmp0'}
          description: Successful request
      summary: Slack Archive Conversation
  tmp1:
    post:
      description: Broadcast message to everyone in the channel or conversation
      parameters:
      - description: Public, private  or IM channel to send message to. Can be an
          encoded ID, or a name.
        example: C1234567890 or mychannel or G012AC86C
        in: query
        name: Channel
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: The title of the message
        example: New Incident
        in: query
        name: Title
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: The message body
        example: IR-23 was created on 1/12/15
        in: query
        name: Message
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {$ref: '#/components/schemas/tmp1'}
          description: Successful request
      summary: Slack Broadcast Message
  tmp2:
    post:
      description: Create A Conversation
      parameters:
      - description: Name of the public or private channel to create
        example: mychannel
        in: query
        name: Channel Name
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Create a private channel instead of a public one. If set to True
          a private channel is created,otherwise a public channel is created.
        example: True or False
        in: query
        name: Is Private
        required: false
        schema: {type: boolean}
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {$ref: '#/components/schemas/tmp2'}
          description: Successful request
      summary: Slack Create A Conversation
  tmp3:
    post:
      description: Get The History of a Specific Conversation by Channel ID
      parameters:
      - description: Channel Name to fetch history for
        example: random
        in: query
        name: Channel Name
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Include messages with latest or oldest timestamp in results only
          when either timestamp is specified
        example: True or False
        in: query
        name: Inclusive
        required: false
        schema: {type: boolean}
      - description: Creates a time range that extends back X minutes ago. (Default
          is 30)
        example: '5'
        in: body
        name: Minutes Ago
        required: false
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Limit the number of conversation objects returned per request.
          (Default is 10)
        example: '9'
        in: body
        name: Limit Results
        required: false
        schema: {type: string}
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {$ref: '#/components/schemas/tmp3'}
          description: Successful request
      summary: Slack Get Conversation History
  tmp4:
    post:
      description: Get Current Usernames In A Conversation
      parameters:
      - description: Name of the conversation to retrieve usernames for.
        example: C1234567890
        in: query
        name: Channel Name
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Limit the number of usernames returned per request. (Default
          is 10)
        example: '9'
        in: body
        name: Limit Results
        required: false
        schema: {type: string}
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {$ref: '#/components/schemas/tmp4'}
          description: Successful request
      summary: Slack Get Users In A Conversation
  tmp5:
    post:
      description: Invite a User or List of Users to a Conversation
      parameters:
      - description: The channel that the users will be invited to.
        example: random
        in: query
        name: Channel Name
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: A list of usernames(s) to invite to a conversation.
        example: username1,username2,username3
        in: query
        name: Usernames
        required: false
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: A group to invite to a conversation.
        example: MyNewUserGroup
        in: query
        name: Group Name
        required: false
        schema: {type: string}
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {$ref: '#/components/schemas/tmp5'}
          description: Successful request
      summary: Slack Invite Users to A Conversation
  tmp6:
    post:
      description: Remove Users from a Conversation
      parameters:
      - description: The channel that the users will be removed from.
        example: random
        in: query
        name: Channel Name
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: A list of usernames(s) to remove from a conversation.
        example: username1,username2,username3
        in: query
        name: Usernames
        required: false
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: A group to remove from a conversation.
        example: MyNewUserGroup
        in: query
        name: Group Name
        required: false
        schema: {type: string}
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {$ref: '#/components/schemas/tmp6'}
          description: Successful request
      summary: Slack Remove Users
tags:
- {name: Communication}
